<p><strong>别亦难</strong></p>
<p>人生若只如初见</p>
<p>何事秋风悲画扇</p>
<p>老院又闻青草香</p>
<p>顿足惆怅若纳兰</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20200828/a8dc78b442f54557ac4c17371ff304a2.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p><strong>星醉</strong></p>
<p>夜幕凄凄</p>
<p>雨袭薄帘</p>
<p>君心谁怜</p>
<p>伴饮一碗</p>            <div class="lookall-box">
<div class="lookall-shadow"></div>
